        SQLITE
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-center justify-center gap-x-2 border-2 px-3 py-2 border-zinc-400 rounded-full text-md">
        GIT
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-center justify-center gap-x-2 border-2 px-3 py-2 border-zinc-400 rounded-full text-md">
        GITHUB
      </li>
